from util import util
import numpy as np
$$\begin{align} c_0 &= 2.5 x^2 \\ c_1 &= 0.3 + 0.8 x \end{align}$$

Model 1:

$$\begin{align} \hat{c}_0 &= w^2 x \\ \hat{c}_1 &= 0.5 |w| \end{align}$$

Model 2:

$$\begin{align} \hat{c}_0 &= w x \\ \hat{c}_1 &= 0.5 \end{align}$$

Model 3:

$$\begin{align} \hat{c}_0 &= w x \\ \hat{c}_1 &= 0.1 - w x \end{align}$$
